<p>So last night I&#8217;ve been paid and now I am in a spending mood.</p>

<p>I am having trouble deciding what MP3 player to get. I want it:</p>

<ul>
<li>small</li>
<li>be able to store <span class="caps">GPG</span> key etc on it</li>
<li>able to access it from my Debian system easily</li>
</ul>

<p>I went to &#8220;JB Hifi&#8221; in Melbourne and:</p>

<ul>
<li>Sadly didn&#8217;t see the <a href="http://liw.iki.fi/liw/log/2005-09.html#20050924b">Yepp</a></li>
<li><a href="http://www.iriver.com.au/iriver/index.cfm?pageID=2&amp;sID=2&amp;prodID=8&amp;">Iriver H10</a> 6G is 396AUD and the 5G is 357AUD. It&#8217;s about the same size as the Ipod mini. Still I think it might be too big&#8230; I do like the FM radio feature though.</li>
